replies.body:
My favorite siege comp conists of {{champion:14}} {{champion:90}} {{champion:26}} 

Sion top or jungle, Malzahar mid, Zilean support. Once you all get a core item just go mid put space aids and a bomb on a minion then launch it into the enemies face with Sion. First off with the base damage of Sion e and Zilean e you can get up to 600 add Malzahar e and it goes up to 920, thats max rank base damage, you can apply this on 1 guy whilst doing 300-600 damage to other champs nearby. This iis pure base damage, and its low cooldown aswell. Add in some ap for Zil and Malz maybe liandries for Malz and relays for ZIlean your poke become more and more unbearable, the later the game goes ^^

Man if you hit the enemy wave clear with 1 space aids isis minion you chunk him so hard he will have to base, Come late you can possibly just outright kill an enemy mage if they dont have much hp or mr with 1 of these Aidsbomb minions.

This is a side effect of the fact that they've systematically nerfed CC and buffed safety and mobility. 

There was a time once when you could send a Sion and Garen bot, and have almost 5 seconds of lockdown if you let gaze hit you with Garen close enough. 

Those were the days.{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-popcorn}}

To everyone complaining/talking about Morde {{champion:82}} 

The only things that made Morde bot lane viable are his XP advantage (why Rito?) and his ghost dragon. You want him bot lane because you can get dragon and have that major siege power.

Morde plus Zilean is stupid :P
